import { Grid } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import Topics from '../component/Topics';

function Member(){
    return (
        <Grid>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Grid.Column width={3}>
                    會員選單
                </Grid.Column>
                <Grid.Column width={10}>
                    <Routes>
                        <Route 
                            path='my/history'
                            element='歷史分析'
                        ></Route>
                        <Route 
                            path='my/settings'
                            element='會員設定'
                        ></Route>
                    </Routes>
                </Grid.Column>
                <Grid.Column width={3}></Grid.Column>
            </Grid.Row>
        </Grid>
    );
}

export default Member;
